<div class="section-content section-5">
    <div class="gr-12">
        <div class="gr-row">
            <div class="gr-12">
                <h1>
                    [% l("How to trade binaries?") %]
                </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="first subsection">
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <a name="binary-trading-in-3-easy-steps-section"></a>
                    <p>
                        [% l("Trading binaries is remarkably easy, and requires only 3 simple steps:") %]
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-row">
                    <div class="gr-4">
                        <img class="ja-hide responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-1.svg') %]"/>
                        <img class="hidden ja-show responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-1-jp.svg') %]"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gr-4">
                        <img class="ja-hide responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-2.svg') %]"/>
                        <img class="hidden ja-show responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-2-jp.svg') %]"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gr-4">
                        <img class="ja-hide responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-3.svg') %]"/>
                        <img class="hidden ja-show responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-3-jp.svg') %]"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-row">
                    <div class="gr-4">
                        <p class="center-text">
                            <strong>
                                [% l("Define your position") %]
                            </strong>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gr-4">
                        <p class="center-text">
                            <strong>
                                [% l("Get your price") %]
                            </strong>
                        </p>

                    </div>
                    <div class="gr-4">

                        <p class="center-text">
                            <strong>
                                [% l("Make your trade") %]
                            </strong>
                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <a name="define-your-position-section"></a>
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Step 1: Define your position") %]
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        [% l("First, you need to set the parameters of your trade. Here's what you need to consider.") %]
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <img class="ja-hide responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/get-started/define-your-position.svg') %]"/>
                    <img class="hidden ja-show responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/get-started/define-your-position-jp.svg') %]"/>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Choose a trade type") %]
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <p class="ja-hide">
                        [% l("<strong>Rise/Fall</strong> - predict if the market will rise or fall from its current level.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("<strong>Higher/Lower</strong> - predict if the market will end higher or lower than a price target.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("<strong>Touch/No Touch</strong> - predict if the market will touch or not touch a price target.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("<strong>In/Out</strong> - predict if the market will stay inside two price targets, or end between or outside them.") %]
                    </p>

                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Choose the underlying market") %]
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <p>
                        [% l("<strong>Currencies</strong> - trade all major FX pairs.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p class="ja-hide">
                        [% l("<strong>Stock Indices</strong> - trade all major worldwide stock indices.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p class="ja-hide">
                        [% l("<strong>Commodities</strong> - trade major commodities such as gold and oil.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p class="ja-hide">
                        [% l("<strong>Volatility Indices</strong> - trade [_1]'s proprietary volatility indices.", website_name) %]
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Choose the duration") %]
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-3 gr-4-m gr-centered gr-padding-10 ja-hide">
                    <img class="responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/get-started/duration.svg') %]"/>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <p>[% l("You can set the length of your trade, from 10 seconds to 365 days.") %]</p>
                    <p>[% l("But there's no need to wait until expiry. You can sell back long-term trades at any time to profit from changing market conditions.") %]</p>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Choose the barrier(s)") %]
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-6 gr-7-m gr-centered gr-padding-10 ja-hide">
                    <img class="responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/get-started/barriers.svg') %]"/>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <p>
                        [% l("The barrier(s) you choose defines your position and triggers your payout.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("You set the barrier(s) to define your position.") %]
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Choose the payout") %]
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-5 gr-8-m gr-centered gr-padding-10 ja-hide">
                    <img class="responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/get-started/payout.svg') %]"/>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <p>
                        [% l("Each binary trade is for a pre-determined payout amount. You win the payout if your prediction is correct.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("You can choose payouts from \$1 to \$50,000. This wide payout range is ideal for both small and large traders.") %]
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="subsection hidden">
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <a name="get-your-price-section"></a>
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Step 2: Get your trade price") %]
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        [% l("[_1] prices are benchmarked against the interbank options market, so you always get best-in-class prices for your trades.", website_name) %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("You get fair and transparent pricing, whatever your position.") %]
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection hidden">
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <a name="make-your-trade-section"></a>
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Step 3: Make your trade") %]
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        [% l("When you are satisfied with the trade price, instantly execute your trade.") %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("With [_1]'s unique platform, there's no risk of 'slippage' or gapping markets. And no hidden fees.", website_name) %]
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        [% l("You can sell back long-term trades at any time to profit from changing market conditions.") %]
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection last hidden">
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <a class="by_client_type client_logged_out" name="dont-just-read-about-it-section"></a>
                    <h2>
                        [% l("Interested? Why not try a virtual account") %]
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        [% l("Test-run [_1], and sharpen your trading skills, with a no-risk, no-commitment, virtual account.", website_name) %]
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <div class="gr-row">
                        <div class="gr-4">
                            <img class="responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-1.svg') %]"/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gr-4">
                            <img class="responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-2.svg') %]"/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gr-4">
                            <img class="responsive" src="[% request.url_for('images/pages/home/step-3.svg') %]"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12">
                    <div class="gr-row">
                        <div class="gr-4">
                            <p class="center-text">
                                <strong>
                                    [% l("Define your position") %]
                                </strong>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gr-4">
                            <p class="center-text">
                                <strong>
                                    [% l("Get your price") %]
                                </strong>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gr-4">
                            <p class="center-text">
                                <strong>
                                    [% l("Make your trade") %]
                                </strong>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gr-12 gr-padding-10 center-text by_client_type client_logged_out">
                    <a class="button pjaxload" href="[% request.url_for('/') %]">
                        <span>
                            [% l("Try it now") %]
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <p>
                        [% l("No risk, \$10K virtual money account") %]
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gr-12 center-text">
                <div class="subsection-navigation">
                    <br/>
                    <a class="back button" href="#">
                        <span>[% l("Back") %]</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="next button" href="#">
                        <span>[% l("Next") %]</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
